\n到而家都未走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果季開頭排左好耐榜尾 最後又咪順利前四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個季真係傳奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但亦都係劇本嘅序章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9f33bdb33d266302b65a9f8718a5f0b2f6c69b","tid":48650,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T10:56:06.000Z","msg":"我都希望見到雲加係酋長教到斷氣"}]}